Install Node.js and dependencies
================================================

To install dependencies:

`apt install composer`
`composer install`

Also from `node` folder (script tested on Ubuntu):

`./install-node`



Tune and run Node application
================================================

Important backend part is a node application.

1) You need to specify port to listing in `node/app.js` and same at `config.php`

2) There is a script to run process as a service
To start: `./start-node`


Tune Config.php
================================================
Copy `config.example.php` to `config.php` and tune

1) You should specify same port as at the node app, admin address, fee in procents
